### Get all books (public endpoint, no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a book by ID (requires USER role)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic user user

###

### Get a book by ID that does not exist (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic user user

###

### Create a new book (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin admin

{
  "isbn": "978-0134685991",
  "title": "Effective Java",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "publishedDate": "2018-01-06"
}

###

### Create another book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic librarian librarian

{
  "isbn": "978-0596517748",
  "title": "JavaScript: The Good Parts",
  "author": "Douglas Crockford",
  "publishedDate": "2008-05-01"
}

###

### Create a book with invalid payload (validation error - 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin admin

{
  "isbn": "invalid-isbn",
  "title": "",
  "author": "Unknown",
  "publishedDate": "2099-01-01"
}

###

### Update an existing book (requires authentication)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin admin

{
  "title": "Effective Java (3rd Edition)",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "publishedDate": "2018-01-06",
  "status": "BORROWED"
}

###

### Update book status to AVAILABLE
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic librarian librarian

{
  "title": "Effective Java",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "publishedDate": "2018-01-06",
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Delete a book (requires ADMIN role)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Authorization: Basic admin admin

###

### Delete a book without ADMIN role (403 Forbidden)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/2
Authorization: Basic user user

###

### Access protected endpoint without credentials (401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Accept: application/json
